  [2]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String
  [3]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_objects/Object/values
  [4]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys
  [5]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Data_structures

